{"tid":483484,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(廚刀)想買一把自用西廚刀(旬shun)，求意見","createTime":"2017-11-29T07:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T04:43:53.000Z","uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"50f0fec96d63aa8fead5bc05da6c3e6fd081f8db","tid":483484,"uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"首先我係一個home cook啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶定頭盔先<br />\n屋企有一把70蚊嘅文武刀，我有用磨刀石嘅習慣，所以基本上係無乜問題。<br />\n但我最近想嘗試西式廚刀，買一把主廚刀嚟挽下。<br />\n我心目中簡左呢把<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Shun旬 主廚刀 8吋</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ss-knife.com.tw/images/product/m/shun_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ss-knife.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2Fm%2Fshun_4.jpg&h=983c1729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本刀好似有信心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n筆直$1200-$1400<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thank you"},{"pid":"c0e82b3cf4081fce5edd7f9bdccce7731166fbc9","tid":483484,"uid":27172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"28dbcd09ae63f191350d172b20010d8dd3ffa59c","tid":483484,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3848fb511ea935bdea987e01f4e490fb42da31b4","tid":483484,"uid":61295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d7522a27b68f5ea8500aed9b415e475d149c435","tid":483484,"uid":13959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"三叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d065f313e7961917d7ae2756c3b79f531c2b5820","tid":483484,"uid":14640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"